{
  "stem": "10960.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So I said to the SS man, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "These are the alphabet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "These people, they are alphabet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They don't know to read German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Please read it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So he took it over from my hands, and he read it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He said, that's good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It said, it's sufficient.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It's enough.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Let's go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I had twice.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I had twice-- two times-- even the-- that's what I-- then when they are day-- was the second day was just-- and the-- and the Judenrein.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "When he came back from work, he said, you know what we have now?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And we saw it through the windows, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "The way such a cultural country took upon themselves to-- to destroy a nation from 6 million Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Why did they do it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "What wrong did we do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We're decent people, educated people, obey the rules, pay the taxes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Must be a reason.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "No any other reason according to my mind-- Hitler was a maniac.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this is what the people didn't understand.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that is the reason when he felt a little bit better, he found out to kill, to take suicide.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he suicided.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But where-- where was the world?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After that, we went-- when he came from work, he told us we have to go a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They prepared and made it very fast.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said in-- in-- if any Jews remained, they shall go there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's already prepared-- you know, closed up, where there was a needle wires.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A ghetto.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] is in Polish, called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But a ghetto-- ghetto in English.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And everybody who remained has to go there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they shall come to the Judenrat and register themselves.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
